This is a placeholder for the raylib static library.

To build raylib for macOS:
1. Download raylib source from https://github.com/raysan5/raylib
2. Build: make PLATFORM=PLATFORM_DESKTOP
3. Copy src/libraylib.a to this directory

Or use CMake:
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
make
cp src/libraylib.a ..
